HEADWORD: Coralwort
<hw>Cor"al*wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A cruciferous herb of certain species of <gen>Dentaria</gen>; --
called also <altname>toothwort</altname>, <altname>tooth
violet</altname>, or <altname>pepper root</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

